The ideal outcome would be the tab with empty fields gets navigated and error messages display.

To reproduce this problem:
Say I have a very basic form as follows:

```
class ExampleForm(forms.Form):
    field_one = forms.CharField(required=True)
    field_two = forms.CharField(required=True)

